Author: chezpajama
Text: Mitsuwa sells konjac jelly and shirataki.  Zion market has kimchi, seaweed snacks etc  Both are in Kearny Mesa.

Author: unsurebanana
Text: I don't know if you already have all this where you're from but popcorn! Best brands are boom chicka pop, skinny pop, and my favorite is Half-Naked popcorn (24 cal per cup) but it's so so good. I eat them by misting them with water and adding curry powder and salt and it's amazing. Also, loving almond milk right now.
